Zambia Won’t Seek Partner for Oil Refinery, Daily Mail Reports

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-11-29T11:46:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/zambia-won-t-seek-partner-for-oil-refinery-daily-mail-reports.html
Zambia  won’t seek a partner to
operate its sole oil refinery, Indeni, after  Total SA (FP)  sold a 50
percent stake in 2009, the Lusaka-based  Daily Mail  reported,
citing Energy and Water Minister Christopher Yaluma.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony Mukwita in Johannesburg at 
 amukwita@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  